(8, 'SMART IT FEST COMPETITION 2022', '7eb0d826-b819-48f4-875f-b089d4bc1360.jpg', '<p>PROUDLY PRESENT &ndash; Sebelas Maret Information Technology Competition atau biasa disingkat SIC merupakan agenda tahunan dari D3 Teknik Informatika Universitas Sebelas Maret untuk mengapresiasi karya-karya dari masyarakat di seluruh Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>SIF Competition tahun ini bertema &ldquo;Ready to Color the Future&rdquo; dengan arti siap untuk mewarnai masa depan menggambarkan kesiapan D3 Teknik Informatika yang untuk memulai inovasi-inovasi baru dalam bidang teknologi informasi. Kesiapan dalam memulai inovasi baru berkaitan dengan Dies Natalis D3 Teknik Informatika tahun 2022 yang ke 20 tahun yang tentunya menggambarkan kematangan dan kedewasaan untuk mengambil keputusan dalam mempersiapkan masa depan yang penuh warna.</p>\r\n<p>Lomba kompetisi yang akan mewarnai rangkain SIC diantaranya :<br>1. Lomba&nbsp;<strong>Start Up</strong><br>2. Lomba&nbsp;<strong>App Dev</strong><br>3. Lomba&nbsp;<strong>Short Movie</strong></p>\r\n<p>Pendaftaran Lomba Start Up:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://bit.ly/PendaftaranLombaStartUpSIF2022\">Pendaftaran Lomba StartUp SIF2022</a></p>\r\n<p>Pendaftaran dan Pengumpulan Lomba APPS DEV:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://bit.ly/DaftarAppsDevSIF2022\">Daftar AppsDev SIF2022</a></p>\r\n<p>Pendaftaran Lomba Short Movie</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://bit.ly/PendaftaranLombaShortMovieSIF2022\">Pendaftaran Lomba ShortMovie SIF2022</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide Book &amp; Contact Person :<br>LOMBA STARTUP<br>link: https://bit.ly/StartUpSIF2022<br>cp: wa.me/6285849540204 (Daaniis)</p>\r\n<p><br>SHORT MOVIE<br>link: https://bit.ly/ShortMovieSIF2022<br>cp : wa.me/6285259553669 (Ariela)</p>\r\n<p><br>APPS DEV<br>link: https://bit.ly/AppsDevSIF2022<br>cp: wa.me/6285607347220 (Meilinda)</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Ready to color the future&rdquo; bersama kami? Ikuti terus kami di @smartitfestofficial yaa..&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>E-Mailkomp 2022<br>Pemuda Aktif dan Kreatif</p>\r\n<p>Media E-Mailkomp<br>IG : @emailkompuns<br>FB, Twitter : @emailkompsvuns<br>Line : @545zhkbq<br>Youtube : E-Mailkomp SV UNS<br>Web : emailkomp.mipa.uns.ac.id</p>\r\n<p>Media SMART IT FEST<br>FB : Smart Itfest<br>IG : smartitfestofficial<br>Email : <a href=\"mailto:smartitfestofficial@gmail.com\">smartitfestofficial@gmail.com</a></p>\r\n<p><img class=\"img-fluid w-100\" style=\"object-fit: cover;\" src=\"https://d3tisolo.vokasi.uns.ac.id/public/storage/images/1684275628.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"724\" height=\"724\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'SMART IT FEST COMPETITION 2022', '2022-07-15 05:20:00', 'Published', '2022-06-09 05:14:14', 'Humas D3TI-UNS', 'smart-it-fest-competition-2022', 'SMART IT FEST COMPETITION 2022', 6, '2023-05-16 22:21:58', '2023-06-22 02:08:53'),
(9, 'APICS 2022 ‚Äì CALL FOR PAPERS', '1d1ffbeb-8908-4c7c-b485-c2a6dcec56a3.png', '<p><strong>CALL FOR PAPERS APICS 2022</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; The 1st International Conference on Smart Technology, Applied Informatics, and Engineering. The 1st APICS 2022 is a prestigious international platform that brings together academicians, researchers, engineers, professionals, and industrial participants around the world to discuss and share knowledge about their research findings, innovative ideas, and experiences to advance the field of Information Technology, Data Engineering, Artificial Intelligence, Smart Technology, Applied Informatics, and Advanced Engineering.</p>\r\n<p><strong>PUBLICATION</strong><br>1. APICS 2022 Conference Proceeding<br>2. Accepted papers will be submitted for possible inclusion subject to IEEE Xplore&rsquo;s scope and quality requirements and expected to be indexed by SCOPUS.<br>3. Selected papers will be considered for publication in IJAI &ndash; Sinta national reputable journal (https://jurnal.uns.ac.id/ijai)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Virtual Conference</strong>: Surakarta, Indonesia; Tuesday to Wednesday (23-24th August 2022)<br>Theme: &ldquo;Driving Digital Transformations toward Society 5.0 through Smart Technology and Artificial Intelligence&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Important Dates:</strong><br>Full Manuscript Deadline: 10th July 2022 (extended)<br>Notification of Acceptance: 21st July 2022<br>Early Bird Registration Due: 28th July 2022<br>Final Camera Ready: 12th August 2022<br>Regular Registration Due: 12th August 2022<br>Conference Day: 23-24th August 2022<br>Paper submission link: https://apics.i-kaigi.com/login</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information,</strong><br>Visit: https://apics.uns.ac.id/<br>Email: apics@mail.uns.ac.id<br>CP: +6285702401789 (Hartatik)<br>+6281226736944 (Nurul)</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"img-fluid w-100\" style=\"object-fit: cover;\" src=\"https://d3tisolo.vokasi.uns.ac.id/public/storage/images/1684275821.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"794\" height=\"1226\"></p>', 'APICS 2022 ‚Äì CALL FOR PAPERS', '2022-08-24 05:24:00', 'Published', '2023-05-17 05:25:27', 'Humas D3TI-UNS', 'apics-2022---call-for-papers', 'The 1st APICS 2022 is a prestigious international platform that brings together academicians, researchers, engineers, professionals  and industrial participants around the world', 2, '2023-05-16 22:25:47', '2023-06-21 05:50:02'),
